<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>桃花浅浅江湖酸菜鱼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">独家秘制酸菜鱼年销售量10W+</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">桃源仙境风你get到了吗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200902/044753046ce9401c93a4e5bac9d70f3c.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200902/4885e53b0c8545a380fb6996729a1b57.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>招牌酸菜鱼，一年卖出10W+条</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200902/d996aa449f104eed933339d96d6c5ab8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>“鲜活鲈鱼，当天宰杀”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200902/a163ed1b96f94243b64bc9d08af04d54.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">坚持选用新鲜鲈鱼，当天新鲜到店进行宰杀，鲜活乱蹦到师傅都“手足无措”。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>“3mm的鱼片，轻薄透光”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200902/4a1feb03a53b43ae83ea5f659fc06712.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">//</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200902/f79d45e0a75e4962ac5b1e6f7054aec5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">由师傅片出厚薄适中的无骨鱼片，这手法这刀功，每片均能保持在3mm左右，拿起来的瞬间，鱼片超级，轻薄透光。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>“秘制酸菜，灵魂辅菜”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200902/d80c46b009414ff7b956c19e3e77364f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200902/1f5636fd13a2497580e14d790019ee0d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200902/fe91e6529eb54758a2855038f1e45432.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">酸菜均由自己去老坛泡制，脆爽无比。每一份酸菜鱼的灵魂就是它的酸菜，造就了独一无二的酸爽可口，经过大火翻炒的酸菜加入汤中，更将酸味进一步提升。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>“热油浇灌，滋啦作响”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200902/90fa4903a0594cb386c7b7df1e4afa39.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">辣椒花椒热油烹饪，鲜美激发，200度的热油淋漓而下，滋啦作响，香味直接席卷了整个厨房，闻到都咽口水了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>“餐前喝汤，酸辣可口”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200902/8373450b2bd5491da0deab8bce88d5ca.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200902/e7968b9109f845faa19305cce6830cc1.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200902/e7968b9109f845faa19305cce6830cc1.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200902/e7968b9109f845faa19305cce6830cc1.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">端上来先喝汤，融合了鱼的鲜、酸菜和柠檬的酸、花椒的辣，那一份鲜辣酸爽的口感，让你顿时食欲大开。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>“满到快要溢出来的鱼肉”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200902/ba76b1609bb34602b1ec656e28f6ef3d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200902/e40b0250216748b29dddda92ab9ea2f5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200902/a481a4a0465c49ff99b6be13ad06893f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200902/a481a4a0465c49ff99b6be13ad06893f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">料足到你装了满满当当一碗还有多。鲜嫩雪白的鱼肉，肉质清甜细腻没有腥味，当然还有灵魂酸菜不能错过，吃到根本停不下来。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200902/5ae2fa4bff3f4cdd99976995cbc8eaeb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200902/7b6364d189434413b00d9255907d3a1c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">除了招牌的酸菜鱼，还有其他可口的菜品满足你的一切需求。让你吃的更加多样化，超值超抵超满意。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>口水鸡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200902/5d843b3d089144f083a6561c7f210f0c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200902/e7133b980f724a9b924f24f62aa9fbe8.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200902/7dd9b1095b8248bd8b18eb818810f0f8.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">用的是超有名的清远鸡，剥开表面，里面的肉质粉嫩Q弹，蘸上酱汁，入口柔嫩爽口，酸辣解腻，果然是第一名的实力。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>“Duang到不行的我要吃豆腐”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200902/b399bd06c19c4d40a7bc2ab16e484632.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200902/b3cd881f0ea24291b219a34a8831fc50.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200902/600b45d6e23546149c279f6ae6f1dec9.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">嫩滑的日本豆腐在勺子里DuangDuang的超犯规！淋上酱汁吃，不开玩笑的，我能拿来下两碗饭！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>“解辣解腻，超级奈斯”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200902/2f7caf3173b847a6b1eb21340f8600f9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200902/2354eff7a94f4bdc90ee5d7d0eb0c40b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200902/0d093aa37e4a430aa15922e55691be13.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200902/075cf8363aa04e1d9838ea8052af4353.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">嫩绿的上汤豆苗不仅能帮你缓解酸菜鱼带来的一些辣意，还能荤素均衡搭配哦，补充一些维生素，口感爽脆而带有点回甘，也是解腻的不二选择哦。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200902/41bdda02988c498b80a906f38fc3e522.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">/</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">酸</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">梅</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">汤</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">/</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">酸甜可口的酸梅汁，每天新鲜熬制，让你喝完还想再来一杯呢。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200902/bfb5e366982a4b8eb8369318f079d69b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>打卡火爆全网的桃园仙境风</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200902/1be0b8099ebe427eb35163262679dbec.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200902/fb6e8d66724a4300bfe7096628036bc9.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200902/90e050986cc54db5a0bc81108c97c174.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200902/8b12a2c2fc2b46bdb0e99fe8ff6f357f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">入门就感受到了满满的古风，桃花主题的细节随处可见，壁画也恰到好处的古色古香，穿上古装过来吃饭，真的感觉自己身处桃源仙境...</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200902/bff46f8d7d39436ebef765612a829abc.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">／在法律允许范围内，活动解释权归品牌所有／</p>
